                    "Size limit reached for a nibble slice"
                );
            }
        }
        if (keyLen != 0) {
            key = data.decodeBytesN(keyLen / 2 + (keyLen % 2));
            key = Nibble.keyToNibbles(key);
            if (keyLen % 2 == 1) {
                key = key.substr(1);
            }
        }
        return key;
    }
}


